100 Hottie, Amanda Lauren!|date=2019-02-02|website=INSCMagazine|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://mmm.dk/eksklusivt-interview-med-amanda-lauren-jeg-er-paa-maxim-s-liste-over-de-hotteste-kvinder.11630.html|title=Eksklusivt interview med Amanda Lauren: Jeg er p\u00e5 MAXIM\u00b4s liste over de hotteste kvinder|last=Damer {{!}} 9|first=Skrevet af Simone Klindt {{!}}|last2=3K|website=mmm.dk|language=da|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.magzter.com/share/mag/16005/334759|title=Playboy Sweden-March 2019 - Get your Digital Subscription.|website=Magzter|language=en|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://theinscribermag.com/glamour-girl-philly-philly-q-and-a-with-maxim-100-hottie-amanda-lauren/|title=Glamour Girl! Philly Philly! Q and A With Maxim 100 Hottie, Amanda Lauren!|date=2019-02-02|website=INSCMagazine|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref> \n\n== Early life ==\nBruce was born in [[Cherry Hill, New Jersey]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://patch.com/new-jersey/gloucestertownship/watch-nj-woman-ex-charlie-sheen-girlfriend-now-waits-see-if-she-has-hiv|title=WATCH: N.J. Woman, Ex-Charlie Sheen Girlfriend Now Waits To See If She Has HIV|date=2015-11-22|website=Gloucester Township, NJ Patch|language=en|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref> She began her career as a trained nurse<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.inquisitr.com/2579971/amanda-bruce-charlie-sheens-ex-girlfriend-explains-why-she-had-unprotected-sex-after-learning-his-hiv-status/|title=Amanda Bruce: Charlie Sheen's Ex Girlfriend Explains Why She Had Unprotected Sex After Learning His HIV Status|website=www.inquisitr.com|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref>.   After moving to [[Los Angeles]], she met actor [[Charlie Sheen]], who she had a relationship with for 8 months.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.inquisitr.com/2576471/a-nurse-had-unprotected-sex-with-charlie-sheen-knowing-he-was-hiv-positive/|title=A Nurse Had Unprotected Sex With Charlie Sheen Knowing He Was HIV Positive|website=www.inquisitr.com|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ibtimes.co.uk/who-amanda-bruce-meet-nurse-who-had-unprotected-sex-charlie-sheen-knowing-his-hiv-status-1529569|title=Who is Amanda Bruce? Meet nurse who had unprotected sex with Charlie Sheen knowing his HIV-status|date=2015-11-19|website=International Business Times UK|language=en|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref> \n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n\n\n[[Category:1984 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n\n{{Improve categories|date=April 2020}}\n[[Category:Nurses]]\n[[Category:American models]]\n", "text_old": "<!-- Please do not remove or change this AfD message until the discussion has been closed. -->\n{{Article for deletion/dated|page=Amanda Lauren Bruce|timestamp=20200412073405|year=2020|month=April|day=12|substed=yes|help=off}}\n<!-- Once discussion is closed, please place on talk page: {{Old AfD multi|page=Amanda Lauren Bruce|date=12 April 2020|result='''keep'''}} -->\n<!-- End of AfD message, feel free to edit beyond this point -->\nAmanda Lauren Bruce, (born November 28th,1984) is an American model and nurse.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dailyentertainmentnews.com/breaking-news/amanda-bruce-charlie-sheens-ex-girlfriend/|title=Amanda Bruce Charlie Sheen's Ex-Girlfriend (Bio, Wiki)|date=2015-11-19|website=DailyEntertainmentNews.com|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/charlie-sheen-s-ex-partner-on-why-she-had-unprotected-sex-despite-knowing-about-hiv-positive-status-a6740451.html|title=One of the women Charlie Sheen had unprotected sex with speaks out|date=2015-11-19|website=The Independent|language=en|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://people.com/celebrity/amanda-bruce-had-unprotected-sex-with-charlie-sheen-despite-hiv/|title=Nurse Admits to Knowingly Having Unprotected Sex with HIV-Positive Charlie Sheen|website=PEOPLE.com|language=EN|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref> She has been featured i n publications including the cover of [[Playboy]], and a feature in [[Maxim (magazine)|Maxim (magazine),]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.maximitalia.it/amanda-lauren-amo-i-social-ma-non-gli-haters/|title=Amanda Lauren: amo i social ma non gli haters|last=Novembre 2018|first=Maxim Italia 13|date=2018-11-13|website=Maxim Italia|language=it-IT|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://theinscribermag.com/glamour-girl-philly-philly-q-and-a-with-maxim-100-hottie-amanda-lauren/|title=Glamour Girl! Philly Philly! Q and A With Maxim 100 Hottie, Amanda Lauren!|date=2019-02-02|website=INSCMagazine|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://mmm.dk/eksklusivt-interview-med-amanda-lauren-jeg-er-paa-maxim-s-liste-over-de-hotteste-kvinder.11630.html|title=Eksklusivt interview med Amanda Lauren: Jeg er p\u00e5 MAXIM\u00b4s liste over de hotteste kvinder|last=Damer {{!}} 9|first=Skrevet af Simone Klindt {{!}}|last2=3K|website=mmm.dk|language=da|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.magzter.com/share/mag/16005/334759|title=Playboy Sweden-March 2019 - Get your Digital Subscription.|website=Magzter|language=en|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://theinscribermag.com/glamour-girl-philly-philly-q-and-a-with-maxim-100-hottie-amanda-lauren/|title=Glamour Girl! Philly Philly! Q and A With Maxim 100 Hottie, Amanda Lauren!|date=2019-02-02|website=INSCMagazine|language=en-US|access-date=2020-04-14}}</ref> \n\n== Early life ==\nBruce was born in [[Cherry Hill, New Jersey]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://patch.com/new-jersey/gloucestertownship/watch-nj-woman-ex-charlie-sheen-girlfriend-now-waits-see-if-she-has-hiv|title=WATCH: N.J. Woman, Ex-Charlie Sheen Girlfriend Now Waits To See If She Has HIV|date=2015-11-22|website=Gloucester Township, NJ Patch|language=en|access-date=2020-04-12}}</ref> She began her career as a trained nurse<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.i